<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_523" id="261r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_523_r1l20">
<del rend="strikethrough">Joh </del> Hercʒog <expan>Johanſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_523_r1l21"><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> Als vns ewr <expan>hochwird<ex>ikeit</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat / von ewrs gelegers </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_523_r1l22">vvegen / Als Jr ew cʒu velde getan habt von gemains frids vnd nucʒes </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_523_r1l23">vvegen / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd als Jr an vns begert / ob vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_523_r1l24">icht hörten / das <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>cʒuſchade<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht / daʒ vvir ew das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_523_r1l25">cʒevviſſen <expan>tete<ex>n</ex></expan> daſſelb vvir alſo gern tun vvöllen / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvo eʒ <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_523_r1l26">glücklich vnd wol ging / des vvern vvir mitſampt <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden fro vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_523_r1l27">hörten das cʒemal gern / vnd wo vvir auch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> lıeb dinſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_523_r1l28">vnd <expan>wolgeualle<ex>n</ex></expan> beweiſen möchten / des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvir vvıllig vnd teten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_523_r1l29">das allcʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> poſt <expan>Mıchael<ex>is</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_523" id="261r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Johans<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> als uns ewr
                            <expan>hochwird<ex>ikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat von ewrs gelegers wegen,
                        als ir ew czu velde getan habt von gemains frids und nuczes wegen, das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>; und als ir an uns begert, ob wir icht
                        hörten, das <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>czu schade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht, daz wir ew das cze wissen
                                <expan>tete<ex>n</ex></expan>, dasselb wir also gern tun wöllen,
                                <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wo ez <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> glücklich und wol ging, des wern wir
                        mitsampt <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden fro und hörten das czemal gern.
                        Und wo wir auch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> lieb, dinst und
                            <expan>wolgevalle<ex>n</ex></expan> beweisen möchten, des
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wir willig und teten das allczeit
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n.</expan>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> post <expan>Michael<ex>is.</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
